        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <a href="https://www.twitter.com/">
            <span>Twitter</span>
            <img src="https://image.flaticon.com/icons/png/512/3128/3128212.png" alt="" width="30px" height="30px">
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/">
